item.title: CVE-2020-9227|2024-08-04T10:19:20.067Z -- huawei -- moana-al00b
item.description: Huawei Smart Phones Moana-AL00B with versions earlier than 10.1.0.166 have a missing initialization of resource vulnerability. An attacker tricks the user into installing then running a crafted application. Due to improper initialization of specific parameters, successful exploit of this vulnerability may cause device exceptions.
